channel.title: Uploading cache?
channel.description:

Thanks.

item.title: Uploading cache?
item.dc:creator: @Fat_Cookies Fat Cookies
item.description:
@Fat_Cookies wrote:

123lol321:

some give me a fast website to use instead of rapidshare

You cannot use RapidShare anyway because you need a direct link. If you want a free solution http://fileden.com/ are not too bad but you only get 5gb bandwidth/month so if your cache is downloaded 250+ a month it may be a problem.
